  "texts": [
    "Using semantic labels as direct prompts for tuning image input might be inspiring and efficient for some designers, but also comes with risks of concessions of user agency and failing users' expectations of AI's descriptive capabilities.",
    "This may let users desire a more straightforward way of control rather than choosing an expressive way of interaction.",
    "When designing DesignPrompt, we encountered similar trade-offs.",
    "Users depend on system interpretation to enable specific actions, such as utilizing semantics recognized for searching.",
    "However, they also have reservations about excessive system interpretation as they desire their intentions to be accurately conveyed."
  ],
